#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.mul.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.mul"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill:1
#: of
msgid ""
"Return Multiplication of series and other, element-wise (binary operator "
"`mul`)."
msgstr "返回 Series 和 other 的逐元素相乘结果（二元运算符 `mul`）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill:3
#: of
msgid ""
"Equivalent to ``series * other``, but with support to substitute a "
"fill_value for missing data in one of the inputs."
msgstr ""
"等价于 ``series * other``，但支持在其中一个输入中缺失数据时使用 fill_"
"value 替代。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill
#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill:8
#: of
msgid ""
"Fill existing missing (NaN) values, and any new element needed for "
"successful Series alignment, with this value before computation. If data "
"in both corresponding Series locations is missing the result will be "
"missing."
msgstr ""
"在计算前，用该值填充已有的缺失值（NaN）以及 Series 对齐所需的新元素。如果"
"两个 Series 对应位置都为缺失值，则结果也为缺失值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill:13
#: of
msgid ""
"Broadcast across a level, matching Index values on the passed MultiIndex "
"level."
msgstr "在指定级别上进行广播，匹配传入的 MultiIndex 级别上的索引值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill
#: of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill:17
#: of
msgid "The result of the operation."
msgstr "运算结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_series_fill
#: of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

